    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343340/extras/5f3de80c4637038d3ef9fca0c7f6ed47.poster.avif?t=1713626674\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343340/extras/5f3de80c4637038d3ef9fca0c7f6ed47.webm?t=1713626674\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343340/extras/5f3de80c4637038d3ef9fca0c7f6ed47.mp4?t=1713626674\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>&quot;I Can See You&quot; 让你沉浸在令人毛骨悚然的第一人称视角恐怖体验中，精心编织自美国偏远地区家庭入侵的真实案例。这款游戏不仅仅是一场旅程，而是一场每一个阴影都在低语危险的考验。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343340/extras/47ed3fc15442ac7f5565219aee0c47c6.poster.avif?t=1713626674\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343340/extras/47ed3fc15442ac7f5565219aee0c47c6.webm?t=1713626674\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343340/extras/47ed3fc15442ac7f5565219aee0c47c6.mp4?t=1713626674\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点：</h2></strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>最先进的图形：</strong>游戏采用先进的 Lumen 和 Nanite 技术，提供超现实的 AAA 视觉效果，让每一刻都栩栩如生。<br></li><li><strong>沉浸式用户界面设计：</strong>我们采用了极简、现代、干净的用户界面，强调游戏与现实的无缝融合。<br></li><li><strong>通过环境叙事：</strong>故事通过场景本身展开——探索和互动你的周围环境，揭开隐藏其中的令人毛骨悚然的故事。<br></li><li><strong>强烈的恐怖体验：</strong>模拟家庭入侵的恐怖，这款游戏考验你的神经——躲避、制定策略，必要时与看不见的敌人对抗。<br></li><li><strong>生存策略：</strong>在这款游戏中，你是猎物，生存意味着快速思考。你的选择有限且至关重要，因此每一步都很重要。<br></li><li><strong>全球通用性：</strong>支持多种语言，包括英语、德语、葡萄牙语、西班牙语、法语、中文、日语和俄语，欢迎来自世界各地的玩家。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343340/extras/5a425ff711ff7f6230bc69f0112a4794.poster.avif?t=1713626674\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343340/extras/5a425ff711ff7f6230bc69f0112a4794.webm?t=1713626674\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343340/extras/5a425ff711ff7f6230bc69f0112a4794.mp4?t=1713626674\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>&quot;I Can See You&quot; 不仅仅是一款游戏；它是一种生存训练，对你的感官和智慧的挑战。你能否生存下去？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343340/extras/da0b8324a09b90491d90592fc60ac85d.poster.avif?t=1713626674\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343340/extras/da0b8324a09b90491d90592fc60ac85d.webm?t=1713626674\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2343340/extras/da0b8324a09b90491d90592fc60ac85d.mp4?t=1713626674\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
